        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-af5c0ca8-d66f-4b5d-b7c5-1b0464524e33">
                The Prime Minister (Sir Winston Churchill)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-af5c0ca8-d66f-4b5d-b7c5-1b0464524e33" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
